author: Joe Giglio | NJ Advance Media for NJ.com
title: NFL Week 5: Our experts pick each game
text:
Comments 
Week 5 is upon us, NFL fans. 
With four weeks in the books, the narratives and themes of the 2015 season have taken shape. Now, with Colts-Texans about to kickoff the fifth week of games, we're learning more about each team and campaign. 
During each week of the 2015 season, our experts will weigh in with picks for the week. I'll be joined by the beat writers for each of the NFL teams ( Eagles , Giants and Jets ) covered by NJ Advance Media. 
Chime in below in the comments section with your thoughts and be sure to track our progress throughout the year!|
